    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement4"><![CDATA[<p>Click on the <em>Button</em> and <em>DropDown </em>menu will be opened. Clicking on each menu item and the message 'Menu Item has been clicked!' will be shown.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement5"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui <em>Button </em>contains the <em>DropDownMenu </em>property that defines shortcut on the <em>ContextMenu</em>. The assigned menu  that are opened with click on the button.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement3" />
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2" />
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1" />
  </Nodes>
</Data>
